"{\"uid\": \"themoscowtimes.com-2024-05-17-putin-rejects-macron-call-for-ukraine-ceasefire-during-olympics-a85155\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Russian President Vladimir Putin suggested on Friday that Moscow would not comply with calls for a ceasefire in Ukraine during the Summer Olympics, pointing to what he said was the unfair treatment of Russian athletes.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 17, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"score\": 0.995646735028217, \"rank\": 0.004372298746742636, \"text\": \"Russian President\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\"}, {\"begin\": 18, \"end\": 32, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8154290138617864e-19, \"text\": \"Vladimir Putin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vladimir_Putin\"}, {\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 64, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"score\": 0.9999999536498774, \"rank\": 4.4018878364705626e-08, \"text\": \"Moscow\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\"}, {\"begin\": 112, \"end\": 119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9989166099326585, \"rank\": 0.0010843386081502919, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked during a visit to China whether he backed French President Emmanuel\\u00a0Macron's idea for a global \\\"Olympic truce\\\" during the games in Paris this summer, Putin said: \\\"I think these Olympic principles, including the 'Olympic 