ay's international sporting officials are themselves disobeying the principles of the Olympic charter.\\\"\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 592, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He accused sports bodies of \\\"not allowing our athletes to perform at the games with our banner, flag and our national music, our anthem.\\\"\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are committing violations against us and demand fulfillment from us.\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dear friends: we will not get far that way.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 851, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No one has ever come to an agreement that way,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"French President Emmanuel Macron restated on Friday his idea of \\\"an Olympic truce so that Russia ceases its current operations\\\" in Ukraine.\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 1049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 910, \"end\": 926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1000, \"end\": 1006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999849085829361, \"rank\": 1.4882818745994566e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1041, \"end\": 1048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9989166099326585, \"rank\": 0.0010843386081502919, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Russia plans to hold a rival sporting event in September after being barred from competing as a nation in the Olympics - along with ally Belarus - due to its invasion of Ukraine.\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999849085829361, \"rank\": 1.4882818745994566e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1221, \"end\": 1228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9989166099326585, \"rank\": 0.0010843386081502919, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macron thanked Chinese President Xi Jinping last week for backing the idea of a truce in all conflicts, including Ukraine, during the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1231, \"end\": 1237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.085037743504585e-19, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1246, \"end\": 1263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xi_Jinping\", \"score\": 0.9993317924803096, \"rank\": 0.0006686543194867478, \"text\": \"Chinese President\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xi_Jinping\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xi_Jinping\"}, {\"begin\": 1264, \"end\": 1274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xi_Jinping\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xi Jinping\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xi_Jinping\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xi_Jinping\"}, {\"begin\": 1345, \"end\": 1352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9989166099326585, \"rank\": 0.0010843386081502919, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A Message from The Moscow Times:  Dear readers,  We are facing unprecedented challenges.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1470, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1397, \"end\": 1413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Moscow Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Russia's Prosecutor General's Office has designated The Moscow Times as an \\\"undesirable\\\" organization, criminalizing our work and putting our staff at risk of prosecution.\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1471, \"end\": 1477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999849085829361, \"rank\": 1.4882818745994566e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1480, \"end\": 1498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor-General_of_Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999846909994131, \"rank\": 1.5309233400585844e-05, \"text\": \"Prosecutor General\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor-General_of_Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor-General_of_Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1523, \"end\": 1539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Moscow Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This follows our earlier unjust labeling as a \\\"foreign agent.\\\"\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These actions are direct attempts to silence independent journalism in Russia.\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1778, \"end\": 1784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999849085829361, \"rank\": 1.4882818745994566e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The authorities claim our work \\\"discredits the decisions of the Russian leadership.\\\"\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1870, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We see things differently: we strive to provide accurate, unbiased reporting on Russia.\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1958, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1951, \"end\": 1957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999849085829361, \"rank\": 1.4882818745994566e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We, the journalists of The Moscow Times, refuse to be silenced.\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1983, \"end\": 1999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Moscow Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But to continue our work,we need your help.\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your support, no matter how small, makes a world of difference.\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you can, please support us monthly starting from just$2.It's quick to set up, and every contribution makes a significant impact.\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By supporting The Moscow Times, you are defending open, independent journalism in the face of repression.\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2371, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2280, \"end\": 2296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Moscow Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for standing with us.\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2403, \"entities\": []}]}"